            {#</p>#}
            {#</details>#}
            <details>
                <summary class="h4">{% trans %}What to do if I found a bug?{% endtrans %}</summary>

                <p>{% trans %}
                    You can create an issue on
                    <a href="https://github.com/naumovs/instasavegram/issues">github</a> or
                    just use a contact form.
                    {% endtrans %}
                </p>
            </details>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-after">
        <h3>{% trans %}Still have a question? {% endtrans %}</h3>

        <p>
            {% trans with { '%url%': path('contact') } %}
            Send us with a question via the <a href="%url%">contact</a> form.
            {% endtrans %}
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
